2018.problem:
Let $S_1, S_2, \dots, S_{2^n - 1}$ be the nonempty subsets of $\{1, 2, \dots, n\}$ in some order, and let $M$ be the $(2^n - 1) \times (2^n - 1)$ matrix whose $(i, j)$ entry is \[m_{ij} = \left\{
\begin{array}{cl}
0 & \text{if $S_i \cap S_j = \emptyset$}, \\
1 & \text{otherwise}.
\end{array}
\right.\] Calculate the determinant of $M$ .

